]}, {\"sentence\": \"France is at its highest level of security, though officials have repeatedly said there was no specific threat to the opening ceremony or the Games.\", \"from\": 5004, \"to\": 5152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5004, \"end\": 5010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999563443, \"rank\": 3.265389781670281e-11, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But since the last Games - the Winter Olympics held in Beijing in 2022 - wars have erupted in Ukraine and Gaza, providing a tense international backdrop.\", \"from\": 5154, \"to\": 5307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5209, \"end\": 5216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9996939664722264, \"rank\": 0.0003061272129581732, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 5248, \"end\": 5255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999707520151, \"rank\": 1.852344915174802e-08, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 5260, \"end\": 5264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"score\": 0.9482750658531607, \"rank\": 0.05454633999087977, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spectators watching the July 26 opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 5309, \"to\": 5358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: REUTERS  Israeli competitors are being escorted by elite tactical units to and from events and given 24-hour protection throughout the Olympics due to the war in Gaza, officials say.\", \"from\": 5360, \"to\": 5549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5367, \"end\": 5374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"REUTERS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 5376, \"end\": 5383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"score\": 0.8083026045982572, \"rank\": 0.14897658157154592, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\"}, {\"begin\": 5529, \"end\": 5533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"score\": 0.9482750658531607, \"rank\": 0.05454633999087977, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Israel delegation got some boos, but also a lot of cheers, as it sailed by spectators, Reuters reporters saw.\", \"from\": 5551, \"to\": 5664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5555, \"end\": 5561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.897533461446644e-15, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 5642, \"end\": 5649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2296792944683574e-22, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chants of \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cPalestine!\", \"from\": 5665, \"to\": 5688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Palestine!\", \"from\": 5689, \"to\": 5699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5689, \"end\": 5698, \"title\": \"ht